''Multimode 5GHz/2.4GHz (802.11a/802.11b) Dual Band Wireless Router with 4 Ports''
{{SupportPage|vendor=D-Link|model=DI-764}} "GL5254RT-2A2-B10 VER:T1.3" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. This is the same board ID as the [[D-Link DI-624 rev A1]]. The processor is assumed to be a VR4131. The manual says the default SSIDs for both bands are '''default'''.
